  {
    "key": "hero.title",
    "lang": "en",
    "value": "Four decades of foreign trade. A trusted bridge between"
  },
  {
    "key": "hero.titleAccent",
    "lang": "en",
    "value": "Slovakia and China."
  },
  {
    "key": "hero.body",
    "lang": "en",
    "value": "Helping Slovak leaders enter, scale and reposition in China and beyond, guided by the kind of judgement that only comes from doing the work, year after year."
  },
  {
    "key": "hero.title",
    "lang": "sk",
    "value": "Štyri desaťročia zahraničného obchodu. Dôveryhodný most medzi"
  },
  {
    "key": "hero.titleAccent",
    "lang": "sk",
    "value": "Slovenskom a Čínou."
  },
  {
    "key": "hero.body",
    "lang": "sk",
    "value": "Pomáham slovenským lídrom vstúpiť, rozrásť sa a prepozicovať v Číne aj inde, s rozvahou, ktorá sa rodí iba rokmi praxe."
  },
  {
    "key": "quote.primary",
    "lang": "en",
    "value": "Trade is not a transaction. It is a relationship — built across decades, sustained through trust, and measured by what endures long after the contract is signed."
  },
  {
    "key": "quote.primary",
    "lang": "sk",
    "value": "Obchod nie je transakcia. Je to vzťah — budovaný desaťročia, udržiavaný dôverou a meraný tým, čo pretrvá dlho po podpise zmluvy."
  },
  {
    "key": "quote.secondary",
    "lang": "en",
    "value": "贸易不是一笔交易。它是一种关系——跨越数十年建立，通过信任维持，并以合同签署后仍然持续的事物来衡量。"
  },
  {
    "key": "quote.secondary",
    "lang": "sk",
    "value": "贸易不是一笔交易。它是一种关系——跨越数十年建立，通过信任维持，并以合同签署后仍然持续的事物来衡量。"
  },
  {
    "key": "globeIntro.heading",
    "lang": "en",
    "value": "A career mapped across continents."
  },
  {
    "key": "globeIntro.heading",
    "lang": "sk",
    "value": "Kariéra mapovaná naprieč kontinentmi."
  },
  {
    "key": "globeIntro.body",
    "lang": "en",
    "value": "Each pin marks years of work — negotiations, factories, partnerships and the people behind them. Explore the cities that have shaped four decades of foreign trade, with a focus on the relationships built across China."
  },
  {
    "key": "globeIntro.body",
    "lang": "sk",
    "value": "Každá značka predstavuje roky práce — rokovania, továrne, partnerstvá a ľudí za nimi. Preskúmajte mestá, ktoré formovali štyri desaťročia zahraničného obchodu, s dôrazom na vzťahy budované naprieč Čínou."
  },
