    "lang": "en",
    "value": "Consulting for international trade and investments, bridging connections between Slovakia and the Asian market. Stately, Diplomatic, and Precision-Oriented Expertise."
  },
  {
    "key": "footer.tagline",
    "lang": "sk",
    "value": "Poradenstvo v oblasti medzinárodného obchodu a investícií, prepájame Slovensko a ázijský trh. Štátnická, diplomatická a precízna expertíza."
